{
  "info": {
    "name": "MorningAI Core API",
    "description": "MorningAI Phase 3 核心模組 API 測試集合\n\n包含認證系統和推薦系統的完整測試案例。\n\n## 使用說明\n1. 導入此集合到 Postman\n2. 設置環境變數 `base_url` 為 API 服務器地址\n3. 執行 \"用戶登入\" 請求獲取 access_token\n4. access_token 會自動設置到環境變數中\n5. 其他請求會自動使用此 token\n\n## 測試帳戶\n- admin@morningai.com / admin123 (系統管理員)\n- manager@morningai.com / manager123 (租戶管理員)\n- user@morningai.com / user123 (一般用戶)\n- demo@morningai.com / demo123 (Demo 用戶)\n\n## 測試推薦碼\n- WELCOME2025 (admin 擁有，1000次使用)\n- FRIEND50 (manager 擁有，50次使用)\n- DEMO100 (demo 擁有，100次使用)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_postman_id": "morningai-core-api",
    "version": {
      "major": 1,
      "minor": 0,
      "patch": 0
    }
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "認證系統",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "用戶註冊",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"newuser@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"NewUser123\",\n  \"username\": \"newuser\",\n  \"display_name\": \"New User\",\n  \"first_name\": \"New\",\n  \"last_name\": \"User\",\n  \"referral_code\": \"WELCOME2025\",\n  \"language\": \"zh-TW\",\n  \"timezone\": \"Asia/Taipei\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "註冊新用戶帳戶，支援推薦碼功能"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "用戶登入",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const response = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('access_token', response.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refresh_token', response.refresh_token);",
                  "    console.log('Access token saved:', response.access_token.substring(0, 20) + '...');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"user@morningai.com\",\n  \"password\": \"user123\",\n  \"remember_me\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "用戶登入並獲取 JWT 訪問令牌"
          },
          "response": []
        },
